reviews.text: Cozy local farm shop. Christmas market in December.

Nice location, beautiful view. Delicious homemade pastries. Nice shop, both upstairs and Ingela's small flower shop. Also take a look at the garden!
What makes it a great place is that it is atmospheric and personal. Attention has been paid to everything. If we could give a 6 out of 5, we would.
Fantastic place, with good coffee and a great view. Go there.

Incredibly beautiful to sit outside and have a home-baked coffee with a view of the Ånimmen. Very affordable cafe and small nice interior design shop with nice things and good prices! Highly recommend!
Fantastic place with shop and cafe. Good sandwiches and good pastries.
Best place! So knowledgeable and great products. Customer since many years. They also make fine woodwork which they sell. Highly recommended!
Nice staff, such nice cutting boards. And good vegetables.
So fast delivery! Thanks!
Very nice treatment by the 2 Evas. Heh.
Mycket trevligt bemötande.

Fantastic dog kennel in the forest where the dogs run freely and enjoy themselves, which you can rent cheaply. Lots of good dog equipment and lots of nice interiors. Not to forget very friendly service that makes you feel welcome. Strongly recommended.

Old-fashioned shop with small things for the home. Jars, crockery, lamps and decor etc. There is also a department for your best friend, the dog, with a good selection of equipment, toys and more. Always personal service
Eva is so knowledgeable and you always learn something new when you come here. Always ends up more than you planned to buy😅

reviews.text: Very nice place. Very many people, so it is best to book a table if you want to eat. Good food, nice shops.
Fantastic place that must be experienced!
Very cozy! Nice people nice products. Visit the bakery👍. Good waffles, available with shrimp, ice cream and cream 👌. Merry Christmas atmosphere 🎄
There is a lot to look at.
There is a lot to look at, shops of various kinds, exciting with waffles with shrimp on them, I was full and satisfied.
